description: This stylish one-bedroom, one-bath condo in South Boston offers the perfect blend of urban convenience and coastal charm. Located just steps from Broadway's vibrant restaurants, shops, and public transit, and a short distance to M Street Beach, this unit boasts modern finishes including granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an open-concept living space filled with natural light. Enjoy outdoor living on your private deck, newly built in 2022. With a roof updated in 2019 and fresh vinyl siding from 2023, and additional storage in the basement this condo provides both comfort and peace of mind in the heart of Southie.
